Top 5 Eau de Parfums under ₹300 that are perfect
for the season!

♥️ Colorbar Women Ruby Tease 

Ruby Tease is a sweet and fruity aroma, making it suitable for casual outings and daytime wear. The parfum is light and refreshing, with a subtle floral undertone. The sillage is moderate, leaving a subtle scent trail without being overpowering. 
✨Price - ₹660 for 100 ml (Sale Price on Myntra - ₹315)

♥️ Plum BodyLovin’ Smokin’ Vanilla 

Smokin’ Vanilla  is a warm, sweet fragrance that blends vanilla with subtle smoky and musky notes. It’s ideal for evening wear or cooler weather, providing a sensual and inviting scent experience.
✨ Price - ₹345 for 15 ml (Sale Price paid - ₹267)

♥️ Studiowest One Night In Bora Bora 

This perfume features a blend of citrus and fruity top notes, including pear, bergamot, and orange, complemented by floral middle notes of lily of the valley and rose. The base notes consist of musk, moss, ambergris, and patchouli, creating a balanced and refreshing aroma.
✨ Available on Westside. Price - ₹200 for 25ml.

♥️ Nykaa - Joie De Vivre

 “Joie De Vivre,” translating to “joy of living,” offers a lively blend of citrus and fruity notes, reminiscent of a freshly squeezed lemon drink with a hint of zest. It’s likened to the aroma of lemon leaves rather than the juice. The sillage is subtle, making it suitable for daily wear without being overpowering.
✨ Price - ₹279 for 15 ml

♥️ Studiowest 003 Woman 

This perfume opens with a fruity blend of blackcurrant and red fruits, creating a sweet and inviting top note. The heart of the fragrance is floral, adding a touch of elegance and femininity.
✨ Available on Westside. Price - ₹200 for 25ml.

♥️ All these fragrance has a moderate longevity of 3 to 5 hours on the skin.

Introducing @tocobo_official Cotton Soft Sun Stick SPF 50+/PA++++

✨ Tocobo Sun stick offers SPF 50+ PA++++ and contains Herb AC Complex to calm sensitive skin. It controls excess sebum and is an excellent choice for oily skin.

✨ Tocobo Cotton Soft Sun Stick is a physical and chemical sunscreen containing organic and inorganic filters. It is a hybrid sunscreen.

✨ Tocobo Sunscreen Stick Ingredients:
This has chemical filters – Octocrylene (UVB & UVA 11), Octinoxate (UVB), Ethylhexyl Salicylate (UVB), Uvinul A Plus (UVA), Tinosorb S (UVA & UVB), and physical filter – Titanium Dioxide (UVB & UVA 11)

✨ The Tocobo Sunscreen Stick is formulated with Niacinamide, Hyaluronic Acid, Glycerin, Vitamin E and a bunch of Plant Extracts & Oils. It also contains fragrance. So if you are allergic to any of those, please watch out. It does not contain Alcohol though.

✨ Texture: It is a light blue sunstick. It is made of synthetic wax, but doesn’t feel balmy nor waxy. It has a silicone powdery feel to it.

✨ Fragrance: It has added fragrance and as opposed to many, the scent of this sun stick is very subtle to me. It has faint menthol notes that subsides soon after application.

✨ I’d recommend it for its convenient sunscreen application throughout the day. Its zero white cast matte finish will be loved by oily skin types.

✨ Kindly gifted by @maccaron_beauty & @tocobo_official

@laneigeindia Water Bank Blue Hyaluronic Cream Moisturizer is a moisturizer that visibly firms and strengthens the skin’s moisture barrier while delivering long lasting hydration.

It is also formulated with a Zero Irritation Technology, so it's made for those whose skin is prone to heightened sensitivity to certain skincare formulations. The product is slightly scented, but it's barely noticeable once applied.

✨ My Experience - 

The Laneige Water Bank Blue Hyaluronic Cream Moisturizer, contrary to its rich, creamy appearance, the moisturiser is surprisingly very lightweight. It is easy to apply and it felt very moisturising, not sticky or greasy on my normal to dry skin.

📍I used the moisturiser in the morning and evening to see if it can keep my skin hydrated throughout the day. Even after a long day, my skin still feels hydrated in the evening.

📍I used it as a night cream & my face doesn’t feel dry even after waking up in an air-conditioned room.

✨ I highly recommend the Laneige Water Bank Blue Hyaluronic Cream Moisturizer if you have dry to very dry skin and need an extra boost of hydration.

✨ Price - Rs. 3050 for 50ml (currently on discount on maccaron)

✨ Kindly gifted by @maccaron_beauty & @laneigeindia

AD| Introducing @sixam_glow PIVOT THE PORES EXFOLIATOR

A gentle leave-on treatment with salicylic acid to help exfoliate away pore-clogging dead skin cells, prevent blackheads + whiteheads, control oil production and minimize the appearance of pores. It contains green tea extract and sodium hyaluronate to soothe and calm any irritation, and reveal smoother, more hydrated skin.

✨ How to use the exfoliator ? 

📍Use as the first step after cleansing. Gently apply an even layer using fingers or a cotton pad, all over your face. Do not rinse after. Follow it with the rest of your routine.

📍Start slowly - Use it once a week and increase usage to max 3 times a week.

📍Can be used AM and/or PM. Always wear SPF 30+ during the day.

📍Patch test before using.

📍A mild tingling sensation is normal, if excessive irritation occurs, rinse off immediately with cool water.

📍It is gentle enough to be used by all skin types, even sensitive skin.

✨ P.S. - It's fragrance-free!

✨ Price - ₹590

✨ Flat 20% off on PIVOT THE PORES EXFOLIATOR

✨ Available on Six am glow website & Amazon

@isntree Hyaluronic Acid Airy Sun Stick SPF50+ PA++++

This compact sunscreen has been making waves in the K-beauty community, promising a lightweight and moisturizing solution to shield our skin from the sun’s harmful UV rays.

✨ The UV filters in ISNTREE sunscreen stick:

Homosalate (UVB), Octinoxate (UVB), Ethylhexyl salicylate (UVB), Uvinul A Plus (UVA), Tinosorb S (broad spectrum).

Other ingredients: 8 types of Hyaluronic Acid, Niacinamide, Aloe Extract, Pycnogenol, Ceramide NP

✨ My Experience -

This is a Chemical Sunscreen. This sun stick comes in a compact, twist-up tube format. And, I just love the tear drop shape of this sun stick.

It has a very beautiful texture. Feels soft and leaves a beautiful satin finish. It’s not heavy on the skin, but if you apply more than 4-5 layers on the same area, oily skin might feel heavy.

📍Moisturizing texture.
📍Lightweight, Non sticky & Non-Greasy
📍Doesn’t leave white-cast
📍Doesn’t sting my eyes
📍Gives a Satin Finish
📍Alcohol & Fragrance Free
📍It's not Water Resistant

✨ How does it work with makeup?

 In one swipe, nothing happens. However, you are supposed to do it multiple times, and because of the moisturizing formula, it will disturb the makeup to some extent.

✨ Easy to re-apply?

Yes, although it may feel a bit heavier upon re-application, it starts to mattify and become lighter with time.

✨ Who is it for?

The sun stick would suit combination & dry skin types better. Although it mattifies, the base remains moisturizing and can start looking greasy on oily skin in hot, humid weather.

✨ When it comes to my daily sun protection routine, I prefer to reserve sun sticks for re-application only.

✨ Price - Rs. 2438 For 22gm ( Rs.1400 -1600 during sales) 

✨ Available on - @maccaron_beauty
